tagline: RSS thru IM, powered by http://superfeedr.com
body: ### Notifixlite Tired of missing out important updates? Subscribe to your favorite RSS feeds in your IM client with your Google Talk, or Jabber or XMPP client. Just add notifixlite@appspot.com to your contact list. Commands start with /.
